{"tid":1474381,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［重要］我哋需要持久戰  睇完呢個分析 大家識玩啦？","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:23:34.000Z","uid":135762,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a579e41234b3ed66cfbcd9915cdfb3d18355c411","tid":1474381,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:00:06.000Z","msg":"自由的殘體字<br />\n將就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xpVCRn4OvDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxpVCRn4OvDc&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=a8e24c94\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xpVCRn4OvDc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條片主要講<br />\n中美貿易戰 其實邊個揸緊大牌好明顯<br />\n中國每逢有經濟問題 社會問題<br />\n就會大吹雞叫愛大中華<br />\n貿易戰開始  已經開始有愛國社運<br />\n<br />\n依家越嚟越多 #護旗手#撐警<br />\n歷史上鑊鑊都係咁<br />\n依家香港係貿易戰嘅新牌<br />\n要全球支持香港<br />\n就一定要全世界知道中共嘅醜惡<br />\n更多黑材料<br />\n中國其實已經死撐<br />\n好多消息都顯示緊中共內部好多問題<br />\nTrump如果要連任 佢一定要搞好呢單嘢<br />\n同埋片中所講各種因素<br />\n其實我哋係有bargaining power嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我哋出嚟遊行<br />\nFocus喺五大訴求<br />\nBanner 多啲英文<br />\n舉英國 英國 國旗<br />\n唱美國國歌<br />\n要感動美國人民<br />\n要屌鳩英國唔幫我哋<br />\n違反 中英聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\n問題係呢段時間內共匪會唔會反面 攬炒<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n解放軍要落 一定要香港進入緊急狀態<br />\n而且係要有位被人入<br />\n只要我哋KEEP遊行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非好重要</span></span><br />\nbe water 唔好同黑警面對面<br />\n有鬼即捉住 唔好圍 唔好屌 唔好打<br />\n2-3人制服後 就叫記者影<br />\n減少紅媒被造文章<br />\n<br />\n相信嚟緊會放好多鬼喺身邊<br />\n前線都要醒目啲<br />\n唔好以氣用事<br />\n仇恨會使運動失敗<br />\n<br />\n依家黑警有啲已經精神有問題<br />\n其餘嗰啲又武警<br />\n成立獨立調查有啲難<br />\n所以依家主力推721 811恐襲事件<br />\n同埋求美帝幫手<br />\n<br />\n寫多啲唔同英文slogan <br />\n俾多啲外國媒體影到<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以<br />\n再被拉<br />\n再被用私刑<br />\n再失去手足"},{"pid":"200832927d3ee2b4c1144c02cba90c35de68338d","tid":1474381,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"當然向大陸文宣都極重要<br />\n中共要分化<br />\n<br />\n我哋都識！<br />\n<br />\n放啲大陸人見唔到嘅資訊<br />\n入侵百度 微博<br />\n<br />\n你刪一我開十<br />\n<br />\n開啟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中国网络连侬墙</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2260d570c402c53745829ec97511b3b47059c23","tid":1474381,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a8